text: This questionnaire asks questions regarding gastrointestinal (GI) symptoms your child may have experienced. The questionnaire should only be completed by the child's primary caregiver (that is, the person who is responsible for taking care of the child most of the time). If you are not a primary caregiver, please let the staff member know who is so that we may contact that person.

This questionnaire is designed so you can fill it in yourself. There are no right or wrong answers, but please answer each question to the best of your ability. You may choose not to answer questions that make you uncomfortable.
help: Please note that all information is kept strictly confidential
